〈'''Chocolate Love'''〉是[[韓國|韓國]][[女子組合|女子組合]][[少女時代|少女時代]]和[[f(x)_(組合)|f(x)]]為[[LG電子|LG電子]]Cyon[[行動電話|手機]]代言的廣告歌曲。歌曲有兩種版本，音源同於2009年10月8日發表。

== 發行及宣傳 ==
2009年9月15日，[[LG電子|LG電子]]宣佈推出第四個系列“巧克力手機”，並由女子組合[[少女時代|少女時代]]及[[f(x)_(組合)|f(x)]]作為共同代言人<ref>{{cite news |url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0002050983 |title=소녀시대-f(x), 휴대폰 모델 동반 발탁 |publisher=OSEN |language=ko |date=2009-09-15 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113001040/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0002050983 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2009091509111556172&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fko.wikipedia.org |title=소녀시대, 뉴초콜릿폰 광고 맡는다 |publisher=MoneyToday |language=ko |date=2009-09-15 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2018-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001104018/http://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2009091509111556172 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在10月8日，兩種版本的宣傳歌〈Chocolate Love〉公開音源。<ref name=release/>

10月10日，公開兩個版本的廣告片<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kidd.co.kr/news/126070 |title=‘뉴초콜릿폰’ 소녀시대, 에프엑스가 접수 |publisher=산업일보 |language=ko |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2021-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603061518/http://www.kidd.co.kr/news/126070 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002001915 |title='SM선·후배' 소녀시대-f(x), 광고서 매력대결 |publisher=Star News |language=ko |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113001056/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002001915 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，f(x)更於同日舉行的[[Dream_Concert|Dream Concert]]中表演歌曲初舞台<ref>{{cite news |url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=015&aid=0002139179 |title=f(x), 드림콘서트서 ‘초콜릿 러브’ 첫 무대 공개 |publisher=한국경제 |language=ko |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113001058/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=015&aid=0002139179 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月15日，在[[梨泰院|梨泰院]]皇冠酒店邀請了100人參加Showcase，並在當天通過網站發布了音樂錄影帶。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://social.lge.co.kr/product/208_/ |title=달콤한 소녀시대와 짜릿한 에프엑스f(x)의 매력 대결 |publisher=LG Official Website |language=ko |date=2009-10-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=022&aid=0002081740 |title=소녀시대·에프엑스 ‘2그룹2색’ 대결 |publisher=세계일보 |language=ko |date=2009-10-16 |accessdate=2020-04-18 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113001101/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=022&aid=0002081740 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

